The paper proposes a new task of answering questions about personal photos and videos, which involves multimodal data such as images, text, and videos. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a unified network architecture for image, text, and video question answering, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG).
